# Assets Deferred Tax Assets Other Current Amount

## identifier
de8914

## type
float

## definition
This is a balancing item in the list in which it is being used.

This is the value, as at the relevant date, of  Deferred Tax Assets other than those arising out of tax losses that are current. This item is to be determined in accordance with relevant accounting standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.DeferredTaxAssetsOtherCurrent.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo1.02.06
- period=instant
